      <title>欧洲央行行长维勒鲁瓦呼吁灵活调整利率，避免落后于曲线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/ecb-s-villeroy-urges-agility-on-rates-to-not-fall-behind-curve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛表示，欧洲央行必须灵活进一步降息，以避免行动过慢的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/ecb-s-villeroy-urges-agility-on-rates-to-not-fall-behind-curve</guid>
