    <item>
      <title>SEC 指控四家公司淡化与 SolarWinds 相关的黑客攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/sec-accuses-four-firms-of-downplaying-solarwinds-related-hacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四家遭受黑客攻击的公司将支付总计近 700 万美元，以和解美国证券交易委员会的指控，该委员会指控他们淡化了网络攻击的严重性，这是 SolarWinds Corp. 大规模入侵事件的最新后果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/sec-accuses-four-firms-of-downplaying-solarwinds-related-hacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 17:41:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EQT 董事长称地缘政治风险是首要担忧，而非利率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/eqt-chair-says-geopolitics-risk-is-no-1-worry-not-higher-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[EQT AB 董事长康尼·琼森 (Conni Jonsson) 表示，目前世界的地缘政治紧张局势比借贷成本上升的问题更令其公司担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/eqt-chair-says-geopolitics-risk-is-no-1-worry-not-higher-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 17:35:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Applied Nutrition 伦敦 IPO 定价或接近低端水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/applied-nutrition-s-london-ipo-said-likely-to-price-near-low-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，蛋白奶昔制造商 Applied Nutrition Plc 可能会将其在伦敦的首次公开募股 (IPO) 定价为其市场价格区间的低端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/applied-nutrition-s-london-ipo-said-likely-to-price-near-low-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 17:18:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
